HEADWORD: Sea lemon
<hw>Sea" lem"on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
several species of nudibranchiate mollusks of the genus Doris and allied
genera, having a smooth, thick, convex yellow body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

